# /docs/ Directory Structure

The `/docs/` directory contains all necessary documentation to help users, developers, and stakeholders understand and contribute to the AI Virtual Therapist project.

## Directory Contents

```plaintext
/docs/
├── whitepaper.md        # Comprehensive project whitepaper
├── api_reference.md     # Detailed API documentation
├── roadmap.md           # Future development plans and milestones
└── media/               # Visual assets and promotional materials
    ├── branding/        # Logos, color schemes, and marketing materials
    ├── presentations/   # Pitch decks and conference slides
    └── images/          # Project-related images and infographics
